                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable T</hi> 122.) I produce a certificate of Chalk's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted July</hi>, 1845, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months</hi>)—I was present at the trial—he is the person.</p>
